        "created_at": "2021-06-09T01:33:14.684Z",
        "cooked": "<p>What we have tried so far is:<br>\nThe PVC are all restored.<br>\nAll pods started.<br>\nWe manually updated the cluster file in /var/dynamic-conf/fdb.cluster and also updated the ConfigMap.<br>\nWe killed the server process and restart it.<br>\nIn fdbcli, it says it can reach the host but no record in the DB.<br>\nSo, we don\u2019t know what steps do we miss.</p>",
